Mansions in Old Greenwich are selling just days after being listed, David Oglivy of brokerage David Oglivy & Associates.

‘The Old Greenwich market right now is just superhot,’ he said.

About half the buyers are people moving within Greenwich and others are moving from New York City and other areas, he said.

